(70, 1, '2021-06-28 10:00:27', '2021-06-28 09:00:27', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>A good knife is one of the more useful and versatile tools that you can take with you into the backcountry. Not only will a camping knife come in handy when it comes to meal prep and making small repairs to your gear, but it can also be useful when collecting tinder to start a fire, bushwhacking through difficult terrain, and any number of other emergency uses.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In a pinch, a proper knife may even help to fend off a dangerous predator. If you’re in the market for a new camping knife, there has never been a better time to go shopping. There are literally dozens of knives on the market to choose from, coming in a wide array of sizes and with some surprisingly useful options.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sorting through all of those different choices can be confusing, making what should be a simple process a lot more complicated. Fear not, however, as we’ve sorted through the top camping knives that are currently available, identifying the ones that are most worth your time and money. These are our picks for the best camping knives of 2021.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Best Camping Knives of 2021', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'best-camping-knives-of-2021', '', '', '2021-06-28 11:59:57', '2021-06-28 10:59:57', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?page_id=70', 0, 'page', '', 0),
