(309, 1, '2021-07-01 09:33:05', '2021-07-01 08:33:05', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Adventure Blog is more than a website. We are a community of adrenaline enthusiasts who like to share wisdom and experiences. We like to write about everything from upcoming community events to reviewing professional grade gear and equipment.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The Adventure Blog was started in 2007 as a Blogspot and has morphed into a real site with a huge following and a social community full of some of the biggest names in climbing, hiking, exploring biking, traveling, and any other adventures!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Please use the search bar, and you can search through almost 13,000 articles and posts about various topics relating to the adventure world. Please don’t hesitate to <a href=\"https://adventureblog.net/contact-us\">contact us</a> with any questions, comments, or opportunities.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>We are REAL people, with REAL experiences to share. Any writers here are not simply hired guns from a content service; they are genuine adventure junkies who can write!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->		\n												<img width=\"1024\" height=\"683\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-1024x683.jpg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-1024x683.jpg 1024w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-300x200.jpg 300w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-768x512.jpg 768w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, http://localhost/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/giuseppe-mondi-K0VLuATuQ9o-unsplash-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />														\n			<h2>Kraig Becker – Founder, Chief Editor, and Writer</h2>		\n		<p>Kraig is an outdoor and adventure travel writer based in Nashville, TN. Over the course of his career, he has contributed to numerous online and print outlets, including Popular Mechanics<i>, </i>Gear Junkie, Outside Online, National Geographic, Digital Trends, Business Insider, TripSavvy, about.com, and of course The Adventure Blog.</p>\n<p>A lifelong wanderer, his travels have taken him to six continents, traversing mountain ranges, deserts, glaciers, and a host of other environments along the way. He is the author of five books, a collector of backpacks and puffy jackets, and an avid film buff. When he isn’t planning his next adventure, he enjoys running, cycling, hiking, and spending time at home with his wife, who he met at the Brisbane airport in Australia.</p>		\n			<h4>Earnings Disclosure</h4>		\n		<p><strong>Question:</strong> Does The Adventure Blog make money? How?</p>\n<p><strong>Answer:</strong> We are trying! Please help us and support our work.</p><p>We earn in three possible ways:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>The Adventure Blog is a proud partner of the Amazon Associates program. When readers click our affiliate links to Amazon and buy products there, we may earn a commission on qualifying purchases.</li>\n<li>The Adventure Blog is also very proud to be an exclusive member of Mediavine Travel. When readers click on ads delivered by Mediavine, we earn a tiny amount.</li>\n<li>Sometimes product manufacturers have their own affiliate programs or give us free gear to showcase their products. If we highlight their products here, and readers click through to purchase from them, we may earn a possible commission directly from the manufacturer.</li>\n</ol>		\n			<h6>© 2021 The Adventure Blog </h6>', 'ABOUT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '229-revision-v1', '', '', '2021-07-01 09:33:05', '2021-07-01 08:33:05', '', 229, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=309', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
